Nokuthula.Khanyile PHOTO:supplied Grace College’s 2016 Matric pupil, Zenande Sikhakhane, was awarded the Sinclair Trophy for Academic Excellence for being the top pupil at the school in the final IEB Exams. Zenande consistently produced great results over the span of her high school career and we, at Grace College, celebrate her well-deserved four distinctions. (from left) Anele Sikhakhane, Zenande Sikhakhane, Margaret Sikhakhane and Vincent Luksich (Grace College Headmaster).  
